Heya all, hope you're having a great day/night!

This idea just jumped into my head and I instantly I knew I had to post it as soon as I got home, so here I am!
Basically, the idea of the game is that you rate out of ten how well you know the person above you... yeah, that's it.

Have fun and take it easy!
- Aura
